
<h1 class="govuk-heading-l datagovuk-heading-l">Rents, lettings and tenancies</h1>

<section class="govuk-section datagovuk-section">
  <p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">Get the latest data for England from the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government. There are datasets in ODS format for: </p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet datagovuk-list datagovuk-body">
  <li>the number of households on local authority waiting lists since 1987</li>
<li>local authority-owned dwellings let by local authorities since 1981</li>
<li>evictions from local authority-owned dwellings by reason (such as rent arrears or anti-social behaviour) since 2010</li>

</ul>
<p class="govuk-body-m datagovuk-body">You can also download historical or discontinued datasets in ODS or XLSX format on: </p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet datagovuk-list datagovuk-body">
  <li>local authority dwelling stock and average weekly rents, from 2011 to 2019</li>
<li>local authority lettings, by region, from 1988 to 2011</li>
<li>local authority average weekly rents, by district and region, from 1991 to 2023</li>
<li>Private Registered Provider (PRP) average weekly rents, by district, from 1997 to 2023 </li>

</ul>
</section>


